ğŸš€ Getting Started
Prerequisites
bashpip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn jupyter
Running the Project

Clone the repository

bashgit clone https://github.com/yourusername/customer-churn-prediction.git
cd customer-churn-prediction

Install dependencies

bashpip install -r requirements.txt

Launch Jupyter Notebook

bashjupyter notebook Churn_Prediction_Final.ipynb

Run all cells

Execute cells sequentially from top to bottom
Ensure the dataset churn_data.csv is in the same directory



